Odaily Planet Daily News According to Arkham monitoring data, about 8 hours ago, Grayscale transferred about 1,250 BTC and 1,357 ETH at 2 a.m., with a total value of over $127 million, including: 
1. Grayscale Bitcoin Exchange Traded Fund transferred 1,250.606 BTC to two unmarked addresses, worth $123.51 million; 
2. Grayscale Ethereum Exchange Traded Fund transferred 1,357.092 ETH to Coinbase Prime Custody and Deposit addresses, worth approximately $3.779 million.

Odaily Planet Daily News According to the monitoring of chain data analyst Yu Jin, suspected insider traders of LIBRA, a meme token issued by the Argentine president, have made at least 20.18 million through LIBRA. The operations of this address are as follows: 
· In the hours before the tweet was released, USDC and SOL were raised through CEX such as Binance, Bybit, and Kucoin to prepare funds; 
· Sniper buy in the first second after the Argentine president’s tweet was released; 
· Sold all in batches after the market pulled up LIBRA. 
· At least 3 addresses have the same operation.
